---
title: Mexican Black Bean Soup with Charred Corn & Chilli Tortilla Chips
description: One good way to beat the chill? Channel the flavours of Mexico into a hearty soup with black beans and rainbow veggies. A pinch of chilli flakes, some warm tortilla chips and Mexican-style spices bring a summery warmth that'll make you feel toasty inside.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-black-bean-soup-1bab47d2.jpg
